name: AiTools
install_msg:
**Thanks for installing!**
 To use this cog, you will need to get a brain from https://brainshop.ai and `[p]set api brainshopai brain_id <id> brain_key <key>` More information is available here: https://github.com/kaogurai/cogs/tree/master/aitools
description: Talk to a free robot using https://brainshop.ai!
